to take any real responsibility !

963
01:06:06,589 --> 01:06:09,676
That's why you dropped out of school,
why you drop out of everything !

964
01:06:09,884 --> 01:06:11,469
You're pissing your life away !

965
01:06:11,678 --> 01:06:13,388
I don't need the fucking Army....

966
01:06:13,596 --> 01:06:16,141
....and I don't need the war
to tell me that, sir !

967
01:06:16,808 --> 01:06:18,059
Get on your feet, soldier.

968
01:06:19,102 --> 01:06:20,729
Attention !

969
01:06:22,522 --> 01:06:26,192
I don't want you in a stockade.
I don't want you recycled.

970
01:06:26,401 --> 01:06:29,696
I don't want you drummed out
on some bad conduct discharge.

971
01:06:30,989 --> 01:06:34,492
I want you exactly where you are.

972
01:06:35,160 --> 01:06:38,455
And we'll just naturally chew you up.

973
01:06:42,459 --> 01:06:46,046
I'll take care of Wilson.
You get the fuck out of my face.

974
01:07:15,241 --> 01:07:17,369
Sure glad they got Wilson's ass out.

975
01:07:17,660 --> 01:07:19,746
Good riddance to bad rubbish.

976
01:07:19,996 --> 01:07:22,707
- Shut your fucking mouth.
- You shut the fuck up.

977
01:07:22,957 --> 01:07:24,918
- Guys, relax.
- I ain't starting.

978
01:07:25,168 --> 01:07:27,379
You already got your ass beat once.

979
01:07:27,545 --> 01:07:31,466
- Just watch your back in Tigerland.
- I'll do that.

980
01:07:32,759 --> 01:07:36,096
